long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Doodle Jump Trump is an entertaining game available as a Chrome extension. Take control of a character resembling former president Donald Trump and guide him on a jumping adventure. Your objective is to help Trump jump from platform to platform while avoiding obstacles and collecting power-ups along the way. With its simple yet addictive gameplay, vibrant visuals, and catchy music, Doodle Jump Trump offers a lighthearted and amusing experience. See how high you can climb and challenge your friends to beat your score in this whimsical Chrome extension game.

If you want play more game, press Unblocked Games to find more games on our website: https://drivemad.org
